    <div class='row'>
      <h3>Objective</h3>
      <p>
        To build a responsive
        <strong>blog platform</strong>
        for a dog agility brand, using the
        <strong>Noroff API</strong>
        to load dynamic posts and support admin-controlled content. The focus was to combine
        structured front-end fundamentals with API data, authentication, and a clear editorial
        experience.
      </p>
