            <h3>Development Focus</h3>
            <ul class='bullet-list'>
              <li>
                Built with
                <strong>semantic HTML</strong>, structured CSS, and vanilla JavaScript
              </li>
              <li>
                Fetched and displayed blog posts dynamically from the
                <strong>Noroff API</strong>
              </li>
              <li>
                Implemented
                <strong>login and registration</strong>
                for admin content control
              </li>
              <li>
                Created a
                <strong>responsive layout</strong>
                that works across desktop and mobile views
              </li>
              <li>
                Applied
                <strong>accessibility</strong>
                details for navigation, headings, readability, and keyboard use
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class='case-study-wrapper'>
