            <h3>Key Features</h3>
            <ul class='bullet-list-right'>
              <li>
                <strong>Dynamic blog post loading</strong>
                with API-based content
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Admin authentication</strong>
                for creating and editing posts
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Responsive blog layout</strong>
                for desktop, tablet, and mobile screens
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Accessible navigation</strong>
                and structured headings for better usability
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Custom visual identity</strong>
                with agility-inspired graphics and a branded interface
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
